msgid "<b>Book duplicate search</b><br/>- Find groups of books which have an identical identifier such as an ISBN, amazon id, goodreads, uri etc.<br/>- Marking a group as exempt will prevent those specific books from appearing together in future duplicate book searches."
msgstr "<b>圖書重複搜尋</b><br/>- 尋找具有相同識別符號的書籍群組，例如 ISBN、亞馬遜ID、Goodreads、URI 等。<br/>- 將一個群組標記為豁免將阻止這些特定書籍在未來的重複書籍搜尋中一起出現。"

msgid "<b>Book duplicate search</b><br/>- Find groups of books which have a book format that is binary identical.<br/>- Compares the actual file size of every book format in your library, computing an SHA hash to compare contents where sizes match.<br/>- Books found using this search are guaranteed to be duplicates.<br/>- Marking a group as exempt will prevent those specific books from appearing together in future duplicate book searches."
msgstr "<b>圖書重複搜尋</b><br/>- 尋找具有二進位相同的書籍格式的書籍群組。<br/>- 比較您圖書館中每本書籍格式的實際檔案大小，計算 SHA 雜湊值以比較匹配大小的內容。<br/>- 使用此搜尋找到的書籍保證是重複的。<br/>- 將一個群組標記為豁免將阻止這些特定書籍在未來的重複書籍搜尋中一起出現。"

msgid "<b>Title duplicate search</b><br/>- Find groups of books with an <b>identical title</b> and {0}<br/>- Titles must match exactly excluding case.<br/>- Marking a group as exempt will prevent those specific books from appearing together in future duplicate book searches."
msgstr "<b>標題重複搜尋</b><br/>- 尋找具有<b>相同標題</b>且 {0} 的書籍群組。<br/>- 標題必須完全匹配，不區分大小寫。<br/>- 將一個群組標記為豁免將阻止這些特定書籍在未來的重複書籍搜尋中一起出現。"

msgid "<b>Title duplicate search</b><br/>- Find groups of books with a <b>similar title</b> and {0}<br/>- Similar title matches apply removal of common punctuation and prefixes and applies the same title matching logic as Automerge.<br/>- Marking a group as exempt will prevent those specific books from appearing together in future duplicate book searches."
msgstr "<b>書名重複搜尋</b><br/>-查詢具有<b>相似書名</b>且符合 {0} 的書籍分組。<br/>-“相似書名”匹配邏輯會移除常見的標點符號和字首，並採用與“自動合併（Automerge）”相同的書名匹配演算法。<br/>將某個分組標記為“排除”可以防止這些特定的書籍在未來的重複書籍搜尋中再次同時出現。"

msgid "<b>Title duplicate search</b><br/>- Find groups of books with a <b>soundex title</b> and {0}<br/>- Soundex title matches are based on the same removal of punctuation and common prefixes as a similar title search.<br/>- Marking a group as exempt will prevent those specific books from appearing together in future duplicate book searches."
msgstr "<b>書名重複搜尋（Soundex 語音演算法）</b><br/>-查詢具有 <b>Soundex 相似書名</b>且符合 {0} 的書籍分組。<br/>-Soundex 書名匹配同樣會先移除標點符號和常用字首（處理邏輯與“相似書名”搜尋一致）。<br/>-將某個分組標記為“排除”可以防止這些特定的書籍在未來的重複書籍搜尋中再次同時出現。"

msgid "<b>Title duplicate search</b><br/>- Find groups of books with a <b>fuzzy title</b> and {0}<br/>- Fuzzy title matches remove all punctuation, subtitles and any words after 'and', 'or' or 'aka' in the title.<br/>- Marking a group as exempt will prevent those specific books from appearing together in future duplicate book searches."
msgstr "<b>按書名搜尋重複項</b><br/>- 查詢具有<b>模糊匹配書名</b>及 {0} 的書籍分組<br/>- “模糊匹配書名”會移除書名中的所有標點符號、副標題，以及“and”、“or”或“aka”之後的任何詞彙。<br/>- 將某個分組標記為“排除”後，這些特定的書籍將不會在未來的重複項搜尋中同時出現。"

msgid "<b>Author duplicate search</b><br/>- Find groups of books <b>ignoring title</b> with {0}<br/>- Ignore title searches are best to find variations of author names regardless of the books you have for each.<br/>- Marking a group as exempt will prevent any books by those authors from appearing together in future duplicate author searches."
msgstr "<b>按作者搜尋重複項</b><br/>- 在<b>忽略書名</b>的情況下，查詢符合 {0} 的書籍分組<br/>- “忽略書名”搜尋最適合用於查詢作者姓名的不同寫法，而無需考慮您擁有該作者的哪些書籍。<br/>- 將某個分組標記為“排除”後，這些作者名下的任何書籍都將不會在未來的重複作者搜尋中同時出現。"

msgid "an <b>identical author</b>.<br/>- Authors must match exactly excluding case."
msgstr "<b>完全相同的作者</b>。<br/>- 作者姓名必須完全一致（不區分大小寫）。"

msgid "a <b>similar author</b>.<br/>- Similar authors differ only in punctuation, initials or order of their names."
msgstr "<b>相似的作者</b>。<br/>- 相似作者的差異僅限於標點符號、縮寫首字母或姓名的排列順序。"

msgid "a <b>soundex author</b>.<br/>- Soundex author matches start with the same removal of punctuation and ordering as a similar author search."
msgstr "<b>Soundex 讀音相似的作者</b>。<br/>- Soundex 讀音相似作者匹配首先會像“相似作者”搜尋一樣移除標點並統一姓名順序，隨後按讀音進行匹配。"

msgid "a <b>fuzzy match author</b>.<br/>- Fuzzy author matches compare using their surnames and only the first initial."
msgstr "<b>模糊匹配的作者</b>。<br/>- 模糊作者匹配僅對比其姓氏及名字的首字母。"

msgid "<b>ignoring the author</b>."
msgstr "<b>忽略作者</b>"

