msgid "The shorter the soundex length, the greater likelihood of false positives.\nLarge soundex values reduce your chances of matches"
msgstr "Soundex 長度越短，出現誤報（誤判為重複）的可能性就越大。 Soundex 數值越大，匹配成功的機率就越低。"

