msgstr "在標籤瀏覽器中突出顯示作者，以便忽略標題搜尋"

msgid "When checked, will ensure that the authors for the current group\nare shown in the tag browser and highlighted if multiple groups shown.\nOnly applies for author duplicate searches."
msgstr "選中時，將確保當前組的作者\n會顯示在標籤瀏覽器中，如果顯示了多個組，還會高亮顯示。\n僅適用於作者重複搜尋。"

msgid "Sort groups by number of duplicates"
msgstr "按重複次數對組進行排序"

msgid "When unchecked, will sort by an approximation of the title\nor by author if title is being ignored"
msgstr "當取消勾選時，將按標題的近似排序，如果忽略標題則按作者排序。"

msgid "Include languages metadata when comparing titles"
msgstr "比較標題時包含語言後設資料"

msgid "When checked, books with identical titles but different\nlanguages metadata field values will not show as duplicates"
msgstr "勾選此項時，標題相同但語言元資料欄位值不同的書籍將不會被認定為重複項。"

msgid "When doing a Binary Compare, automatically remove duplicate formats"
msgstr "進行二進位制比較時，自動刪除重複格式"

msgid "When checked and the Binary duplicate search is run, if duplicate formats are found\nthen all except one are deleted. The format on the oldest book record will be kept.\nThis is a convenience function for where you have multiple formats associated with\neach book and hence it is not readily obvious which of these is the duplicate.\nNote that the book records themselves are not deleted, and will still appear in the\nresults for merging even if they now have no formats."
msgstr "選中並執行二進位制重複搜尋時，如果發現重複格式\n則除一種格式外，其他格式都會被刪除。最舊賬簿記錄上的格式將被保留。\n這是一個方便的功能，適用於每本賬簿有多個相關格式的情況。\n如果每本賬簿有多個相關格式，而哪個格式是重複的並不明顯，則可以使用此功能。\n請注意，賬簿記錄本身不會被刪除，即使它們現在被合併，它們仍會出現在\n合併結果中。"

