msgid "<b>Book duplicate search</b><br/>- Report books in this library which have an identical identifier for books in the target library.<br/>"
msgstr "<b>圖書重複查詢</b><br/>- 報告本庫中與目標庫中圖書具有相同識別符號的圖書。<br/>"

msgid "<b>Book duplicate search</b><br/>- Report books in this library which are binary identical to books in your target library.<br/>- Compares the actual file size of every book format in your libraries, computing an SHA hash to compare contents where sizes match.<br/>- Books found using this search are guaranteed to be duplicates."
msgstr "<b>書籍重複搜尋</b><br/>- 報告此圖書館中與目標圖書館中的書籍完全相同的二進位制書籍.<br/>- 比較您圖書館中每種圖書格式的實際檔案大小，計算SHA雜湊以比較大小匹配的內容.<br/>- 使用此搜尋找到的書籍被保證是重複的."

msgid "<b>Title duplicate search</b><br/>- Report books in this library compared to your target library with an <b>identical title</b> and {0}<br/>- Titles must match exactly excluding case."
msgstr "<b>標題重複搜尋</b><br/>- 報告此圖書館中與您的目標圖書館具有 <b>相同標題</b> 的圖書 {0}<br/>- 標題必須完全匹配，不區分大小寫."

msgid "<b>Title duplicate search</b><br/>- Report books in this library compared to your target library with a <b>similar title</b> and {0}<br/>- Similar title matches apply removal of common punctuation and prefixes and applies the same title matching logic as Automerge."
msgstr "<b>按書名搜尋重複項</b><br/>- 將當前書庫與目標書庫進行對比，報告具有<b>相似書名</b>及 {0} 的書籍<br/>- “相似書名”匹配會移除常見的標點符號與字首，並採用與“自動合併”相同的書名匹配邏輯。"

msgid "<b>Title duplicate search</b><br/>- Report books in this library compared to your target library with a <b>soundex title</b> and {0}<br/>- Soundex title matches are based on the same removal of punctuation and common prefixes as a similar title search."
msgstr "<b>按書名搜尋重複項</b><br/>- 將當前書庫與目標書庫進行對比，報告具有<b>Soundex 讀音相似書名</b>及 {0} 的書籍<br/>- Soundex 書名匹配首先會像“相似書名”搜尋一樣移除標點符號與常見字首，隨後按讀音進行匹配。"

msgid "<b>Title duplicate search</b><br/>- Report books in this library compared to your target library with a <b>fuzzy title</b> and {0}<br/>- Fuzzy title matches remove all punctuation, subtitles and any words after 'and', 'or' or 'aka' in the title."
msgstr "<b>按書名搜尋重複項</b><br/>- 將當前書庫與目標書庫進行對比，報告具有<b>模糊匹配書名</b>及 {0} 的書籍<br/>- “模糊匹配書名”會移除書名中的所有標點符號、副書名，以及書名中“and”、“or”或“aka”之後的任何詞彙。"

msgid "<b>Author duplicate search</b><br/>- Report books in this library compared to your target library <b>ignoring title</b> with {0}<br/>- Ignore title searches are best to find variations of author names regardless of the books you have for each."
msgstr "<b>按作者搜尋重複項</b><br/>- 將當前書庫與目標書庫進行對比，在<b>忽略書名</b>的情況下報告符合 {0} 的書籍<br/>- “忽略書名”搜尋最適合用於查詢作者姓名的不同寫法，而無需考慮您在各書庫中分別擁有該作者的哪些書。"

